“Where are the Black superheroes?” That question, posed back in 1993, led to a revolution: the creation of Milestone Media.

Milestone introduced comic book readers to the most diverse universe of heroes and villains that the world had ever seen, at a time when characters of color were all too rare in the pages of comic books. Milestone Generations is an incisive look at the company’s rise, outsized impact, and resurgence – just when the world needs heroes more than ever.
